title: To Aru Majutsu No Index Light Novels
description:
This torrent contains Volumes 1-22, SS1, & SS2 from the first series and Volumes 1-10 of New Testament. 

I decided to package this because Baka Tsuki took them down after the novels got licensed in English. I want as many people to be able to experience this great series as possible and I don't think that it should be inaccessible because it got licensed.

Please seed so that people can download it without being limited by my shit upload speed
